The paper discusses the use of neural networks for predicting epileptic seizures from EEG data, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The use of EEG data also suggests a potential connection to neuroscience and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves data analysis and signal processing, which could fall under computer vision (cs.CV) or bioinformatics (cs.BIO).
